PN,31001
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,FThe Cuban government said it shot and
OL,8,Fkilled four Cuban nationals that were
OL,9,Ftravelling aboard a US-registered
OL,10,Fspeedboat on Wednesday.
OL,12,FThey were attempting to enter the
OL,13,Fisland's waters and opened fire on
OL,14,FCuban soldiers, the government added.
OL,16,FCuba had earlier said its soldiers had
OL,17,Fshot four people and wounded six
OL,18,Fothers aboard a Florida-registered
OL,19,Fspeed boat that had entered Cuban
OL,20,Fwaters and injured one Cuban officer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,FThe Cuban government said the majority
OL,8,Fof the people onboard "have a known
OL,9,Fhistory of criminal and violent
OL,10,Factivity" and that they were
OL,11,Fattempting to infiltrate the island
OL,12,Fand commit terrorist acts.
OL,14,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio told
OL,15,Freporters that he was made aware of
OL,16,Fthe incident and that the US is now
OL,17,Fgathering its own information to
OL,18,Fdetermine if the victims were American
OL,19,Fcitizens or permanent residents.
OL,26,@pD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,F"We have various different elements of
OL,8,Fthe US government that are trying to
OL,9,Fidentify elements of the story that
OL,10,Fmay not be provided to us now," Rubio
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
