CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,FThe Cuban government claims to have
OL,8,Fidentified two of the boat passengers
OL,9,Fas Amijail Sanchez Gonzalez and
OL,10,FLeordan Enrique Cruz Gomez, who are
OL,11,Fwanted by Cuban authorities "based on
OL,12,Ftheir involvement in the promotion,
OL,13,Fplanning, organisation, financing,
OL,14,Fsupport or commission of actions
OL,15,Fcarried out in the national territory
OL,16,For in other countries, in connection
OL,17,Fwith acts of terrorism".
OL,26,@qD@MrpqD@XrprD@WrwsD@]OUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,FThe Cuban government also said it had
OL,8,Farrested Duniel Hernandez Santos,
OL,9,Fadding that he was "sent from the
OL,10,FUnited States to guarantee the
OL,11,Freception of the armed infiltration,
OL,12,Fwho at this time has confessed to his
OL,13,Factions".
OL,15,FCuba's government claims it obtained
OL,16,Fthe details about the passengers
OL,17,Faboard the boat from the suspects
OL,18,Fdetained following the shootout.
OL,26,@pD@UrpqD@TOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,FIt identified seven of the ten
OL,8,Fpassengers, while three others have
OL,9,Fnot yet been identified.
OL,11,FIt wasn't immediately known what the
OL,12,Fboat and its occupants were doing in
OL,13,FCuban waters.
OL,15,FPresident Donald Trump's top diplomat
OL,16,Fdeclined to speculate on what
OL,17,Fhappened, saying that it could be a
OL,18,F"wide range of things," and that the
OL,19,FUS will not solely rely on what the
OL,20,FCuban authorities have provided thus
OL,21,Ffar.
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,F"Suffice it to say, it is highly
OL,8,Funusual to see shootouts in open sea
OL,9,Flike that. It's not something that
OL,10,Fhappens every day. It's something,
OL,11,Ffrankly, that hasn't happened with
OL,12,FCuba in a very long time," Rubio said.
OL,14,FHe said both the US Department of
OL,15,FHomeland Security and the US Coast
OL,16,FGuard are investigating the incident
OL,17,Fand stressed that he wants to verify
OL,18,Fthe facts.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,F"The majority of the facts being
OL,8,Fpublicly reported are those by the
OL,9,Finformation provided by the Cubans.
OL,11,F"We will verify that independently as
OL,12,Fwe gather more information, and we'll
OL,13,Fbe prepared to respond accordingly,"
OL,14,FRubio said. "We're going to have our
OL,15,Fown information on this. We're going
OL,16,Fto figure out exactly what happened."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
