PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,FHe said it was not a US government
OL,8,Foperation and that he wasn't "going to
OL,9,Fspeculate about whose boat it was,
OL,10,Fwhat they were doing, why they were
OL,11,Fthere, what actually happened".
OL,13,FRubio said he found out about the
OL,14,Fshooting before the Cuban government
OL,15,Fposted on social media, noting that
OL,16,Fthe US has "constant contact" with the
OL,17,Fcountry "at the Coast Guard level".
OL,26,@sD@^O]xD@LOUxD@]O]yD@IOUyD@bO]
