CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,FUS Vice President JD Vance said on
OL,8,FWednesday afternoon that Rubio had
OL,9,Fbriefed him on the incident, adding
OL,10,Fthat the White House was monitoring
OL,11,Fthe situation.
OL,13,F"Hopefully it's not as bad as we fear
OL,14,Fit could be," Vance said.
OL,16,FThe shooting threatens to increase
OL,17,Ftensions between the US and Cuba
OL,18,Ffollowing the ousting of Venezuelan
OL,19,FPresident Nicolas Maduro.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@MO]{D@Prp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
