OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,FTrump and top administration officials
OL,8,Fhave taken an increasingly aggressive
OL,9,Fstance towards Cuba, which had largely
OL,10,Fbeen kept afloat economically by
OL,11,FVenezuela's oil.
OL,13,FLast month, Trump signed an executive
OL,14,Forder that would impose a tariff on
OL,15,Fany country that sells or provides oil
OL,16,Fto Cuba, despite Cuba's ongoing energy
OL,17,Fcrisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
