PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1772114623
OL,3,CFour people travelling on US-
OL,4,Cregistered speedboat shot dead by
OL,5,CCuban soldiers
OL,7,FMeanwhile, James Uthmeier, Florida's
OL,8,Fattorney general, said he has ordered
OL,9,Fprosecutors to work with federal,
OL,10,Fstate and law enforcement partners to
OL,11,Fstart an investigation.
OL,13,F"The Cuban government cannot be
OL,14,Ftrusted, and we will do everything in
OL,15,Four power to hold these communists
OL,16,Faccountable," he wrote on X.
OL,18,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,19,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,20,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,21,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
